(269, 'Derivada de un logaritmo neperiano', '$$f ( x ) = l n x \\\\f \'( x ) =\\frac{1} x$$', '<p>gñ</p>', 0, 24, '2023-04-22 00:04:19', '2023-06-20 18:32:16'),
